desc: Harness the magical powers of the Caddyshack Putter! As seen in Playboy, USA Today, Golf Digest and Gizmodo. VERY RARE! Makes a great gift for the golfer and movie lover in your life. Whether you're more like Carl Spackler or Ty Webb, you'll walk a little taller when wielding the Caddyshack Putter. -Playboy Magazine
